    <h2>Some useful tips on how to reduce, reuse, and recycle:</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Instead of using plastic, use glass jars, containers, and/ or metal/ reusable water bottles.</li>
        <li>Recycle some water usage for your house plants.</li>
        <li>Encourage an artist! They can use the recycled items to build things like a house or any other resources like a solar panel.</li>
        <li>Instead of paper, we can digitally document everything we need on day to day life.</li>
        <li>When going grocery shopping, use a reusable bag that you bring yourself instead of the plastic bags they have there.</li>
    </ol>

    <table>
