            <td>
                <p>Valdosta average Waste</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Average Population: 56474</li>
                    <li>4.40 lbs * 56,474 people = 248,485.6 lbs of trash produced</li>
                    <li>1.51 lbs * 56,474 people = 85,275.74 lbs of trash recycled</li>
                    <li>Overall: 163,209.86 lbs of trash STILL NOT recycled</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
            <td>
                <p>Valdosta State University average waste</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>The Population of VSU: 11,436 (Average)</li>
                    <li>4.40 lbs * 11,436 people = 50,318.40 lbs of trash produced</li>
                    <li>1.51 lbs * 11,436 people = 17,268.36 lbs of trash recycled</li>
                    <li>Overall: 33.050.04 lbs of trash STILL NOT recycled</li>
                </ul>
            </td>
